  name: BugLevel2
  fishSprite: {fileID: 7042328952989865566, guid: bc77b677fb7e0864ba7648ce7dcb3919, type: 3}
  angryFishSprite: {fileID: 2058498902905776422, guid: d88c04beaa2063f448102c8f38ed2320, type: 3}
  song: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 083ec0ecff9b0424387c625cf503c950, type: 3}
  bpm: 80
  fishname: The Bug
  scientificFishname: Exasperans volatum
  meetingThoughts: "Is this where that buzzing sound was coming from? It seems to
    be some kind of\u2026 bug? It is so rude! It\u2019s definitely affected by [The
    evil wizard fish]\u2019s magic. Regardless of its temperament, it is a creature
    that needs saving.  I really hope that it becomes friendlier once the enchantment
    is removed. "
  journalFishSprite: {fileID: 8875151898643241270, guid: 1fb8d31df5bb3264ba5ec0bc6b70e107, type: 3}
  description: "The Bug is a creature that comes in many shapes, sizes, and colors.
    The most distinguishing features of The Bug are its six legs, compound eyes,
    antennae, and its three-part body. The three parts of The Bug\u2019s body are
    the head, thorax, and abdomen. Rumors in the scientific community tell of a fourth
    part, but it has yet to be substantiated with any meaningful evidence. "
  trinketSprite: {fileID: 3269026354929249442, guid: 421ecc4aa5524944e9b196a723b0e01f, type: 3}
  award1: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d520009bfb2a188479eeec97aa87b6c0, type: 3}
  award2: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d520009bfb2a188479eeec97aa87b6c0, type: 3}
  award3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d520009bfb2a188479eeec97aa87b6c0, type: 3}
  extra1: "I guess it\u2019s true that small packages can have big surprises. "
  extra2: 'Why would nature make something so fierce with such sturdy armor? '
